https://www.tensorflow.org/tutorials/image_recognition

references this repo:

https://github.com/tensorflow/models

and asks you to find classify_image.py:

cd models/tutorials/image/imagenet

which lines up with this:

https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/tutorials/image/imagenet

Please reopen or refile if this is in error. Thanks!
